The paper focuses on developing an intelligent system using machine learning methods for power system stability assessment, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The use of machine learning methods also suggests that the paper could be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves simulations and modeling, which could also place it under software engineering (cs.SE).
